block content
  h1 Percentage of time per project
  p.lead Track the total work remaining and project the likelihood of achieving the sprint goal. This helps your team manage its progress and respond accordingly.
  form.form-inline
    +staff-selector(selectedStaff, staff)
    +time-range-selector(selectedTimeRange, timeRanges)
    button.btn.btn-default(type="submit") Apply
  div Total: #{total} hours
  each percentage in percentages
    div #{percentage.project}: #{percentage.percentage}%
